dct_title_s: 十二万五千分一圖印度及緬甸 / 参謀本部, 印度測量局.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, form lines, rock drawings, and spot heights. Depth shown by soundings in fathoms. Topographic maps showing province or state, district, tribal, township boundaries; some vegetation; graves, oil wells, batlle-fields (with date); places of worship. Based on maps scale of 1:126,720 by the Government of Burma under the Surveyor General of India,1916-1942. "本圖ハ一九二五年印度測量局調製十二万六千七百二十万分一二色刷圖ヲ十二万五千分一二伸寫複製セルモノナリ." "昭和十九年製版・参謀本部," "昭和十七年十一月製版陸地測量部・同十七年十一月発行参謀本部." Issued in quadrangles 30ʹ of longitude by 30ʹ of latitude. Includes index map to adjacent sheets and districts, and lenght conversion table. Title varies: Jūniman gosenbun no ichizu Indo oyobi Biruma -- Jūniman gosenbun no ichizu Biruma oyobi Taikoku -- Jūniman gosenbun no ichizu Biruma oyobi Shina -- Jūniman gosenbun no ichizu Biruma, Shina, oyobi Futsuryō Indo Shina. Title varies: 十二万五千分一圖印度及緬甸 -- 十二万五千分一圖緬甸及タイ國 -- 十二万五千分一圖緬甸及支那 -- 十二万五千分一圖緬甸, 支那及佛領印度支那. Sheets individually numbered: "No. 92F/S.W." Confidential "Hi" printed on upper right margin. "佛領印度支那, 雲南省 - ビルマ, タイ" in upper right margin, and "秘" stamped in upper corner.
